description: The Jungle Chemist Currently Resides In The High Desert Of Central Oregon, But Is From Northern California.. Where He Plans To Return. His Debut Album "Motivation For Levitation" Was Created In 2004, And Has Finally Been Recently Remastered And Released On MP3.COM And Will Be Available Here On ThePirateBay, And In Local Record Stores.
